-<a href="http://www.echoofvalor.org">Echo of Valor</a><br>
-<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=402042">My Magelo</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=donoradanin>donoradanin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#333333>(3/1/03 6:49:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1628.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Neh`Ashiir, the torch, and Shaman Epic turn in</span><hr size=1> Well, I still think your chances are better just killing him straight up. <br>
<br>
out of my 4 CoM raids for Neh'Ashiir, the first 3 had shaman turn ins and no torch.<br>
<br>
The 4th one had no shaman turn in and he dropped the torch.<br>
<br>
so for u unlucky mages out there.. screw the shaman turn in first.)<br>
<br>
I'm sure all mobs have a loot table and if the shaman item is on there, that's one less chance of ur torch dropping. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zyphyr>Zyphyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 898<br> <font color=#333333>(3/2/03 12:57:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1628.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Neh`Ashiir, the torch, and Shaman Epic turn in</span><hr size=1> Based on my personal experince (100+ Neh kills, some triggered some not), the odds for a torch drop are identical whether or not Neh has been triggered for the Shaman epic.<br>
<br>
The non-triggered Neh always drops 2 items : Key of Torsis and one of the following:<br>
1)Ornate Rune Shield<br>
2)Woodsman's Staff (or something like that... a Ranger only 2HB)<br>
3)the torch<br>
<br>
ORS = common, torch = uncommon, staff = rare<br>
<br>
When you trigger Neh, it drops 3 items : Key, The piece for the shaman epic, and one of the 3 items listed above. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:medium;">Zyphyr Runnersbane</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
